<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5380981>
    dc:description "FIG. 19. Jurassinemestrinus eurema (Rhagionemestriidae), new species, holotype AMNH Bu-SE3/3. A. Wing. B. Head, right lateral view. C. Antenna, lateral view. D. Left protarsus, ventral view. E. Posterior portion of thorax and anterior portion of abdomen, oblique dorsal view, showing shapes of scutellum and groove on tergite 1. F. Male terminalia, oblique right lateral view. Panels C, D to same scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5380981/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5381047>
    dc:description "FIG. 51. Jurassinemestrinus eurema, new species (Rhagionemestriidae), holotype AMNH Bu-SE3/3. A. Habitus, right lateral. B. Head and thorax, right lateral. C. Habitus, ventral. D. Head, ventral. E. Right wing. F. Tarsi. G. Male terminalia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5381047/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

